Package sru.edu.group1.workorders.controller

Class WorkOrdersController

java.lang.Object
sru.edu.group1.workorders.controller.WorkOrdersController
@Controller public class WorkOrdersController extends Object
This is the main controller for the project, includes all user, admin, manager, and technician links. Although those may get separated later with the project.
Author:
Trevor Bell trevorbell030@gmail.com, Ellie Wurst, John Friend, Hunter Minteer
